{"tid":856223,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"5000億填左維港效益仲大 好處多多","createTime":"2018-10-10T13:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T16:05:46.000Z","uid":60381,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"977390dcf814a7246219017fca2c134433d80095","tid":856223,"uid":60381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:02:02.000Z","msg":"填東大嶼得1700公頃 即係<span style=\"color: orange;\">17</span>平方公里<br />\n填左維港 填埋右 有<span style=\"color: orange;\">41</span>平方公里<br />\n可以解決房屋問題 又解決埋塞車問題<br />\n冇海就冇埋海港污染問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n維港即使冇左貨物港口世界地位<br />\n應該蝕蝕埋埋嘅錢都冇5000億<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n況且填維港應該冇填外海咁貴<br />\n又可以加強港島九龍地域連繫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲洗乜用咁多錢啫<br />\n一於填鳩左個臭維港佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨低啲錢咪留返比林奠做下禮囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：響應開post bump爆熱門擺創意台<br />\n都幾有創意呀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cef4d2e8ba5288e63ab63d615c0c88bbce7796a","tid":856223,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:03:26.000Z","msg":"應多起一間恒大"},{"pid":"5e9aaae932ea233ad56b76509f428d865641c5d4","tid":856223,"uid":60381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cef4d2e8ba5288e63ab63d615c0c88bbce7796a","tid":856223,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:03:26.000Z","msg":"應多起一間恒大"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:05:04.000Z","msg":"又得啫 起完隨時陸沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e1b6b4c550f10284a7e73f2595a3abc9b91b994","tid":856223,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e9aaae932ea233ad56b76509f428d865641c5d4","tid":856223,"uid":60381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cef4d2e8ba5288e63ab63d615c0c88bbce7796a","tid":856223,"uid":12